[ grunts ]
[ groans ]

04:13.020 --> 04:14.052
tell him about the hats.

04:14.054 --> 04:15.938
Well, early, um...

04:15.940 --> 04:17.239
You tell him, denny.

04:17.241 --> 04:19.157
