them from my cold, dead head!

04:43.600 --> 04:45.417
[ siren wails in distance ]

04:45.419 --> 04:47.185
[ down-tempo music plays ]

04:47.187 --> 04:49.638
[ beeping ]

04:50.724 --> 04:52.357
